」先？<br />\n過唔到嘅即係市場冇人鐘意，咁仲出乜鳩「有深度作品」</blockquote><br />\n口話支持有深度作品 有幾多個真係比錢支持 唔肯比錢然後屌人唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n輕改低成本 又點都有班讀者會買 咁咪越嚟越多 一套紅唔起咪賭第二套會紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c2aa08d6907849a61fe902f947f180293c1f5bb","tid":86662,"uid":80192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十套新番有七套都係輕小說<br />\n唔係肉就賣萌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩撚哂啲毒撚<br />\n少少深度作都出唔到幾套<br />\n觀眾口味又低下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2014之後就無追<br />\n依家得返啲日常番睇得過<br />\n其他都係搵返啲舊番睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好少睇動/漫畫<br />\n入黎只係想睇下你講乜<br />\n感想: 唔係好鐘意見到&quot;萌&quot;之類嘅支那字眼"},{"pid":"6ae4234b9b806cd5b722b382cfeaf4af8c530ca3","tid":86662,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前一季至少追5套<br />\n依家1年都唔知有無一套<br />\n行animate一大半都唔知咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為有一大半係乙女番<br />\n講緊日本嗰個"},{"pid":"496aa038303a82c94578dfb21ab86d28eb3b16b4","tid":86662,"uid":16515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T11:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>十套新番有七套都係輕小說<br />\n唔係肉就賣萌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩撚哂啲毒撚<br />\n少少深度作都出唔到幾套<br />\n觀眾口味又低下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2014之後就無追<br />\n依家得返啲日常番睇得過<br />\n其他都係搵返啲舊番睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好少睇動/漫畫<br />\n入黎只係想睇下你講乜<br />\n感想: 唔係好鐘意見到&quot;萌&quot;之類嘅支那字眼</blockquote><br />\n萌都支那字 你邊到鄉下呀"},{"pi